@startuml
!include ../style.puml

title Kafka High Watermark and Replication

participant Client
box "Kafka Cluster" #LightBlue
    participant "Leader\nNode" as Leader
    participant "Follower 1\nNode" as Follower1
    participant "Follower 2\nNode" as Follower2
end box

' [step1 {"name":"Initial State: All in Sync"}]
note over Leader, Follower2 #E6F3FF
**Initial State**
messages up to offset 9
**High Watermark (HWM): 9**
Log End Offset (LEO): 9
Log:
| 8 |
| 9 |
end note
' [/step1]

' [step2 {"name":"Leader Appends New Message"}]
Client -> Leader: Produce(Message 10)
activate Leader
Leader -> Leader: Append Message 10 to Log
note right of Leader #FFFFCC
**Leader Log Updated**
**LEO: 10**
HWM: 9 (Not yet replicated to quorum)
Log:
| 8 |
| 9 |
| 10 |
end note
Leader --> Client: Ack
deactivate Leader
' [/step2]

' [step3 {"name":"Followers Pull Data", "newPage": true}]
par Followers Fetch
    Follower1 -> Leader: Fetch(Offset 10)
    activate Follower1
    activate Leader
    Leader --> Follower1: Records(Message 10)
    deactivate Leader
    Follower1 -> Follower1: Append Message 10
    note right of Follower1 #E6FFE6
    **Follower 1 Log Updated**
    LEO: 10
    (HWM updated in next fetch)
    Log:
    | 8 |
    | 9 |
    | 10 |
    end note
    deactivate Follower1

    Follower2 -> Leader: Fetch(Offset 10)
    activate Follower2
    activate Leader
    Leader --> Follower2: Records(Message 10)
    deactivate Leader
    Follower2 -> Follower2: Append Message 10
    deactivate Follower2
end
' [/step3]

' [step4 {"name":"Followers Acknowledge & Leader Updates HWM", "newPage": true}]
Follower1 -> Leader: Fetch(Offset 11)
activate Leader
note right of Leader #FFE6E6
**Replication Check**
Leader receives Fetch(11)
⇒ Follower 1 has 10
Leader has 10
Quorum (2/3) reached for Offset 10
**Update HWM to 10**
end note

note right of Leader
Response includes
**HighWatermark: 10**
end note
Leader --> Follower1: Records(Empty), HWM=10
deactivate Leader
Follower1 -> Follower1: Update HWM = 10
' [/step4]

' [step6 {"name":"Client Read Restricted by HWM", "newPage": true}]
Client -> Leader: Consume(Offset 0)
activate Leader
note right of Leader
Leader checks HWM=10
Returns messages 0..10
end note
Leader --> Client: Messages 0..10
deactivate Leader
' [/step6]

' [step7 {"name":"Scenario: Client attempts to read uncommitted", "newPage": true}]
Client -> Leader: Produce(Message 11)
activate Leader
Leader -> Leader: Append 11 (LEO=11)
note right of Leader
HWM: 10
Log:
| 9 |
| 10 |
| 11 |
end note
deactivate Leader

Client -> Leader: Consume(Offset 11)
activate Leader
note right of Leader #Pink
**Read Check**
Request Offset: 11
Current HWM: 10
Log:
| 10 (HWM) |
| 11 |
**Result: Empty/Wait**
(Message 11 exists but is not committed)
end note
Leader --> Client: Empty Response (or wait)
deactivate Leader
' [/step7]

@enduml
